{"title":"bug引题-学习Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api区别","uid":"ed80e4e3f3e8382b0b8f5e494dcfbbef","slug":"Junit_and_junit","date":"2023-12-15T14:42:14.000Z","updated":"2023-12-24T09:47:24.262Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Junit_and_junit.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312152257269.png","content":"<h1 id=\"Junit和Junit-Jupiter-api用法区别\"><a href=\"#Junit和Junit-Jupiter-api用法区别\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api用法区别\"></a>Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api用法区别</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Junit 5 &#x3D; Junit Platform + Junit Jupiter + Junit Vintage</p>\n<p>Junit4中的@Test是import org.junit.Test;<br>Jupiter中的@Test是import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"1-bug引题\"><a href=\"#1-bug引题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. bug引题\"></a>1. bug引题</h2><ol>\n<li><p>今天在学习Spring的时候，整合Spring5-text5测试环境的时候</p>\n<p>@Autowired 一直提示是空指针，搞得我很困惑，@Component没有问题，配置类也没有问题</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@SpringJUnitConfig(value = &#123;testProtoxy.class&#125;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">testioc</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@Autowired</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> Calculator calculator;      <span class=\"comment\">//有接口用接口取</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@Test</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title function_\">testioc01</span><span class=\"params\">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"variable\">add</span> <span class=\"operator\">=</span> calculator.add(<span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">&quot;add = &quot;</span> + add);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>后来百度之后，发现在测试函数上面加一句即可正常运行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">@RunWith(SpringJUnit4ClassRunner.class)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>当然还没有学习到太深，只是靠字面理解这不就是跑在junit4的环境下面吗，那我的依赖</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;dependency&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;groupId&gt;org.junit.jupiter&lt;/groupId&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;artifactId&gt;junit-jupiter-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;version&gt;5.3.1&lt;/version&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/dependency&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>岂不是白白声明到5了</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>我就想起去百度这两个有什么区别的时候，遂产生了此篇记录博客</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"2-学习区别\"><a href=\"#2-学习区别\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 学习区别\"></a>2. 学习区别</h2><p>Junit 5 &#x3D; Junit Platform + Junit Jupiter + Junit Vintage</p>\n<p>Junit4中的@Test是import org.junit.Test;<br>Jupiter中的@Test是import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312152251520.png\" alt=\"image-20231215225144324\"></p>\n<p>在测试类中@Test导入了****Junit.Jupiter.api****的Class文件后，我们就不需要再加上@RunWith注解了</p>\n<p>否则在junit4下，需要如下配置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@RunWith(SpringJUnit4ClassRunner.class)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@SpringJUnitConfig(value = &#123;testProtoxy.class, javaProtoxy.class&#125;)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","text":"由bug引题，学习了Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api区别...","permalink":"/post/Junit_and_junit","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Spring","slug":"Spring","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Spring.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Learn","slug":"Learn","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Learn.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Junit%E5%92%8CJunit-Jupiter-api%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api用法区别</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-bug%E5%BC%95%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. bug引题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 学习区别</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CYLIN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312241427715.jpg","link":"/","description":"多读书多看报，少吃零食多睡觉。","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/479018557"},"email":{"icon":"/svg/email.svg","link":"mailto:1873378495@qq.com"},"qq":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312242201293.jpg"},"leetcode":{"icon":"/svg/leetcode.svg","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/c